reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater soft and comfortable, with a relaxed fit that's not tight around the belly and long enough to wear with leggings.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars So cute and comfortable for fall/winter!
items.body: I bought this sweater from Dokotoo and loved it! The color-block striped design is modern and pairs easily with jeans or leggings. The fabric is soft and good quality; it's not itchy and feels warm without being too heavy. The crew neck fits very well and the cut is slightly loose, making it comfortable and flattering. Ideal for cool fall days and perfect for winter with a jacket over it. The size was as expected (I ordered my usual size). Plus, the colors are just as seen in the photo. I recommend this sweater if you're looking for something cute, casual, and warm for the season. Read more
items.author: Amparito Burbano

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cozy, Stylish, and Perfect for Fall
items.body: This sweater is absolutely beautiful! The material is soft, cozy, and lightweight but still keeps you warm — perfect for fall and winter days. The fit is true to size, very comfortable, and flattering without being too tight or too loose. The brown and white striped design looks stylish and exactly as pictured, making it easy to dress up with jeans or keep casual with leggings. I’ve already received compliments every time I wear it! After washing, it kept its shape and the colors stayed vibrant with no fading or shrinking, which shows the great quality. If you’re looking for a classic, comfortable, and durable sweater, this one is a must-have. Read more

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good looking sweater
items.body: Love sweater. Sweater is warm and cozy. It fits true to size with a little looser fit but not oversized look. Feel put together and fashionable wearing it with jeans. Read more
items.author: Sherri

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Starts Cute - Pills Quickly
items.body: I love this sweater’s style. Super cute stripes, long enough for my tall torso, and cozy - not too thick, but still warm. Where it lost its stars was in quality. At first, it seems great. But within a couple hours of wear, the pilling started. I’ve got a large bust, so it’s mostly noticeable there, but under the arms is pretty significant as well. I’ll try a fabric shaver, but I’m not holding out hope for longevity on this one. 5’6” 150lbs Read more

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Stylish and Comfortable
items.body: I love this sweater! I love the color. I’ve worn it many times. I love it with black jeans. Extremely comfortable and stylish. Read more
items.author: Katie Davis

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super soft!
items.body: Super comfortable and soft! Perfect for a fall day. It’s lightweight, but it keeps you warm enough for a breezy day in the 70s. The length is great for anyone with a long torso. I would say it fits true to size. For reference, I purchased medium - I am 5’5” and 158lbs. Definitely wash with cold water and on delicate to maintain integrity. I would recommend air drying or no heat drying. Read more
items.author: Danielle R.

short_description:
Womens Dress is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

Comfort comes from both the cut and the fabric, so selecting your preferred fit makes a noticeable difference over a full day of wear.

long_description:
Womens Dress is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Blackish Green, A-black Stripe, A-black, Apricot Pink, A-green, Dark Grey, Navy Blue, Beige Stripe, B-pink, A-red Stripe, Desert Palm, Green Stripe, A-brown, Khaki Stripe. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
